{"tid":1684193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］解散警隊 撤回反蒙面法 屬於五大訴求","createTime":"2019-10-31T03:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T04:56:29.000Z","uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5e00e5eb17fad2c542b57b8e227a401937505abc","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"唔好再講四大訴求/六大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n1.<del>撤回送中惡法 </del> 撤回反蒙面惡法<br />\n<br />\n2. 收回暴動定性<br />\n<br />\n3. 釋放抗爭者 撤銷檢控<br />\n<br />\n4. <del>成立獨立調查委員會</del> 解散警隊 追究警暴<br />\n<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n獨立調查委員會其實都係無牙老虎<br />\n南丫海難 地鐵偷工減料都係獨立調查委員會做<br />\n但係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無人需要問責</span></span>"},{"pid":"5d99ba9c253a0cad155babfec0ab79f918f076c3","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:28:32.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"5c60460febdab64db5adf86ee1a4139a2cb3d1b0","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:28:51.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"b1b35c3c384c170ea5033eb0fe12cd0f7ca3b4a3","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:29:09.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"6a7eed90d26670df990d7f4790ded795931b9b92","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:29:19.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"acefc685a37d57c93569b0b2c627e61ba3351bf8","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:29:29.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"179d3fdb1357ee9ceb3e7cb52fa3917a3d39abf1","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:29:39.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"dd036eecd9815b3545bf7bef66e1a631149f6a4c","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:29:49.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"4185f9b3222e56fab4a46a40808cac2a80773b10","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:31:18.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"8118ac6d38f53e1e987260c3b043d671929f290a","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:31:31.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"7ab8a9eeb2339627b94bd111cdce796882831512","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:31:43.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"b00ec8048b7e5a1a1aaede23dc691af072209d1c","tid":1684193,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnAxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=19a4c620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d866b626a4d166027a48dc300b0478cf870ed3","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:54:51.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"d4fa1c915b02068e3b5ab41f74d06048a3b779fb","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:56:19.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"7aae692231d33608171dd057e511084b1486cec8","tid":1684193,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:56:29.000Z","msg":"缺一不可"}]}